				<p>This isn’t learned in a book. It’s cultivated by first-hand experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-4">
        <hr class="mobile-hr">
				<%= image_tag("home_OurFocus_innovation.png", :style => "width:100%; border-radius: 10px")%>
				<p class="mt-4"><strong>3. RESPONSIBLE INNOVATION</strong></p>
				<p>We make sure our impact in the local and global community is a positive one.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
  <div class="flex page-canvas">
    <div class="btns-wrapper">
